ff-road-adventure-bikepacking-fork-with-3-inch-tire-clearance-and-low-axle-crown_testing-700x420.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb20 700w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-263147\">c. Curve Cycling</figcaption></figure><p>Calling their new full-carbon Curve GMX+ fork “a purpose-built fat tire non-suspension corrected bikepacking fork” highlights how niche this really is. But especially to custom framebuilders looking to create the kind of bike that cross continents, the Curve’s carbon GMX+ fork fills a real gap between gravel forks and mountain bike suspension forks.</p><figure id=\"attachment_232577\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-232577\"><a href=\"http://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Curve-GMX_adventure-bikepacking-bike_titanium-off-road-MTB-mountain-bike-gravel-monster-cross-plus-bikepacking-bike_frameset.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Curve-GMX_adventure-bikepacking-bike_titanium-off-road-MTB-mountain-bike-gravel-monster-cross-plus-bikepacking-bike_frameset.jpg\" alt=\"Curve GMX+ adventure bikepacking bike, titanium off-road MTB mountain bike gravel monster cross plus bikepacking bike\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1000\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Curve-GMX_adventure-bikepacking-bike_titanium-off-road-MTB-mountain-bike-gravel-monster-cross-plus-bikepacking-bike_frameset.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Curve-GMX_adventure-bikepacking-bike_titanium-off-road-MTB-mountain-bike-gravel-monster-cross-plus-bikepacking-bike_frameset-297x186.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Curve-GMX_adventure-bikepacking-bike_titanium-off-road-MTB-mountain-bike-gravel-monster-cross-plus-bikepacking-bike_frameset-800x500.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Curve-GMX_adventure-bikepacking-bike_titanium-off-road-MTB-mountain-bike-gravel-monster-cross-plus-bikepacking-bike_frameset-120x75.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor